Instructions for backend functionality
--- New Issue ---
-> activityList for button generation
-> activityList for option generation
-> form for new issue: 
 - take current user as the poster
 - generate date string from now time on server
 - After form submit redirect to comment page

--- Comment ---
-> activityList for button generation
-> commentList for displaying all coments
-> ability to take two inputs:
 - Close Issue - can only be done by the owner if current user is owner button is visible Close/Open
 - Post comment - form text field. Logged in user is added as the commenter, id and date generated, 
   comment linked to the current issue
